# Public, build-time env vars. SAFE to commit — these values are
# inlined into the client JS bundle that every visitor downloads.
# - Supabase URL is just the project endpoint.
# - Supabase anon key is the public key the browser uses; Row Level
#   Security is what actually protects your data, not the key.
# Anything secret (SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY, STRIPE_SECRET_KEY,
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, etc.) lives in Cloudflare Worker secrets — never
# committed.
